window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>You can't wake up if the nightmare is real.</p> <p>Ten-year-old Jason Meechum is a quiet boy who hides in fantasy and science-fiction books. Other kids pick on and make fun of him, but he suffers through it. That's because Jason has a secret. A secret of pain and fear. A secret he wants to tell but can't. All of that is about to change because Jason will be the recipient of something special. Something beautiful, mysterious, wondrous, and odd. Tonight, Jason will be the bearer of two secrets that will meet for the first time. Only one will survive. The outcome will determine if 10-year-old Jason will live to see age 11.</p> <p><i>The Gift</i> is the third in a miniseries of short stories, novelettes, and novellas by Easton Livingston called The Dark Corner. It is a paranormal fantasy novelette. The other stories in the series, \"The Visitor\", <i>The Forest</i>, <i>The Basement</i>, and <i>The Confrontation</i> are available online for download. Easton Livingston is a supernatural, superheroic, and science-fiction author, weaving together action, fantasy, and suspense. Fans of <i>The 4400</i>, <i>Stranger Things</i>, and <i>Fringe </i>television series are sure to enjoy his work. Become an RIU Citizen today. Download <i>The Gift</i> now and begin your journey. A boy. A present. A nightmare. Download your copy of <i>The Gift</i> today.</p>"; 
